
# Index of Generated Files

This index provides a list of all files generated during the class action settlement scan task.

- **master_report.md**: The main report summarizing the findings of the scan.
- **class_actions.json**: The complete raw data of all identified settlements in JSON format.
- **high_value_alerts.txt**: A text file highlighting the high-value settlements with potential payouts over $1,000.
- **classaction_org_settlements.txt**: Raw text data extracted from classaction.org.
- **topclassactions_settlements.txt**: Raw text data extracted from topclassactions.com.
- **23andme_settlement_details.txt**: Detailed information about the 23andMe settlement.
- **ndm_settlement_details.txt**: Detailed information about the Nations Direct Mortgage settlement.
